    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1863-12-10T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1863-12-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="262" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d262">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">A. L.</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                    Chun</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Yarmouth,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1863-12-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">December</hi> 10, 1863.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>A steamer said to be of similar appearance to Chesapeake passed this
                                harbor about noon yesterday, steering down the bay.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>A. L.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
